{"tid":162252,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"狗狗生肉粒","createTime":"2017-03-19T06:40:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-19T09:08:05.000Z","uid":80761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3758d223ff71439a3e76f5461504a806e0a93e02","tid":162252,"uid":80761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T06:40:56.000Z","msg":"迷你牧羊狗 男仔9歲<br />\n啱啱幫佢沖完涼吹毛個陣見到有一粒肉粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人知係咩黎同點解會生肉粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4653436.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4653436.jpg&h=485ca523&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UNawsr2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUNawsr2.jpg&h=d1506aec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6b860867427ab3fca02bf775f9eae0762c44d1ae","tid":162252,"uid":89729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T06:42:13.000Z","msg":"隻狗讀基中？"},{"pid":"a189bf5136f304ba2adc6937f75a28b47be60597","tid":162252,"uid":80761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T06:48:33.000Z","msg":"同埋白色啲毛開始變紅色<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係因為唔夠營養定老既象徵黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/19/144832_e1adecdfec0487f9331ecd1208e376f3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F19%2F144832_e1adecdfec0487f9331ecd1208e376f3.jpg&h=0973aec0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ef51cb474ffced5ae1dadf5c1a54b003d0a4923","tid":162252,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T07:01:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/19/150016_2372bf44a3383c5186d86388d2d668b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F19%2F150016_2372bf44a3383c5186d86388d2d668b3.jpg&h=95148e5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我果隻都有一粒 之前去打針果陣問埋醫生 佢話係暗瘡黎 唔洗理佢 但係好鬼耐都仲係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/19/150112_0fe29f49ae19de7c5223b4d911490743.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F19%2F150112_0fe29f49ae19de7c5223b4d911490743.jpg&h=fd843826&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我依隻又係d毛慢慢變啡 都係九歲左右 應該唔係大問題係老左？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a55e75e0efbdcfba845a71cd918a60d2d2a34c1","tid":162252,"uid":80761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T07:08:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/19/150016_2372bf44a3383c5186d86388d2d668b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F19%2F150016_2372bf44a3383c5186d86388d2d668b3.jpg&h=95148e5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我果隻都有一粒 之前去打針果陣問埋醫生 佢話係暗瘡黎 唔洗理佢 但係好鬼耐都仲係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/19/150112_0fe29f49ae19de7c5223b4d911490743.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F19%2F150112_0fe29f49ae19de7c5223b4d911490743.jpg&h=fd843826&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我依隻又係d毛慢慢變啡 都係九歲左右 應該唔係大問題係老左？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嚇死我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a46197c936da801ceb8ef82ef0855729aa2f985","tid":162252,"uid":61724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T07:10:15.000Z","msg":"男人老狗留指甲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4730f35e039e4a3cbf2ddcd868dba72f47d0e0f","tid":162252,"uid":21122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T07:33:33.000Z","msg":"我隻狗都生左一粒肉瘤係下巴<br />\n之後帶佢睇獸醫<br />\n獸醫話好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果睇唔順眼可以開刀切左佢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後都係開刀算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該係似老人家生肉粒生係臉到咁"},{"pid":"193ba4db2b78269cdf2826318fd4c990f4373b1a","tid":162252,"uid":80761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T09:07:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>男人老狗留指甲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n女朋友黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f37f446ef767e13eaa1a11ed1f5b7c54173ec12c","tid":162252,"uid":80761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T09:08:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我隻狗都生左一粒肉瘤係下巴<br />\n之後帶佢睇獸醫<br />\n獸醫話好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果睇唔順眼可以開刀切左佢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後都係開刀算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該係似老人家生肉粒生係臉到咁</blockquote><br />\n如果冇咩事都唔開刀啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 窮撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}